    "why_it_works": "Digital party packs carry roughly 85% net margins with zero fulfillment cost. Demand runs year-round — birthdays don't have an off-season — though Q4 dips only slightly. The $8–24 price range is low enough to be an impulse buy but high enough to reward quality. Buyers frequently purchase multiple packs for siblings, making repeat sales realistic without extra marketing effort.",
