    "what_to_avoid": "Never base a pack on a trademarked character — no Bluey, Paw Patrol, or Disney references, even stylized. Etsy actively removes these listings and repeat violations risk shop suspension. Avoid packs with too many pieces at launch; a bloated, inconsistent kit reads as low quality. Watch resolution: exports below 300 DPI generate bad reviews fast. Don't undercut yourself below $8 — it signals low value and attracts buyers who leave difficult feedback.",
