    "what_to_avoid": "Avoid offering too many style options in one listing — it slows turnaround and muddies your brand. Buyers sometimes submit blurry or low-angle photos; set clear photo requirements upfront or you will redo work for free. Don't undercharge to compete with AI-only shops; buyers who want hand-illustrated quality will pay for it. Oversaturation is real at the generic end, so a distinct style is your main differentiator.",
