    "what_to_avoid": "Avoid thin, stiff ribbon that photographs well but feels cheap on arrival — reviews will say so. Inconsistent bow sizing within a set is a common quality miss that leads to returns. Don't list sets as handmade if you're reselling wholesale bows without modification; Etsy's handmade policy applies here. Resist copying top-seller colorways exactly — the market rewards distinct palettes, not imitation.",
