    "what_to_avoid": "Do not underestimate how much a confusing instruction sheet will hurt your reviews — it is the single most common complaint in this category. Avoid floss colors that photograph muddy; buyers judge by the listing image. Do not copy patterns directly from other designers. Resist listing too many colorway variants before your core designs have reviews; a thin catalog with strong social proof outperforms a wide catalog with none.",
